p.d: Caroline's rustic existence is shattered when petrol-head, Reeves, drives into her picturesque valley with the purpose of buying her land to build a raceway. Reeves soon discovers country girls are not the push-over he expected and Caroline shows him there is more to life than tarmac and throbbing engines...
